high_descs: Head right to the living room to reach the pink table on the left.
Pick up the box of tissues from the table.
Turn left and walk into the bedroom on the right.
Switch on the floor lamp next to the pink bed.
anns.task_desc: Switch on the light while holding the box of tissues.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the living room.
There is a tissue in the pink colored table.
Take the tissue from the table and go to the bedroom
Put the tissue near the lamp, and the lamp will be glow.
anns.task_desc: Take the tissue from the table and glow the lamp.

high_descs: Leave the room and take a right, and then a right into the living room and go to the pink table.
Pick up the facial tissue box off of the table.
Turn left, then go into to the bedroom on your right and turn on the lamp.
Look at the tissue box in front of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a box of tissue and turn on the bedroom lamp.

high_descs: Enter the hall, go straight, turn right, and then turn right to the tvstand.
take the tissuebox in to table
Move the box and turn right to left on the floorlamp in the room.
Take the box turn right along the floorlamp on the wooden table.
anns.task_desc: Take the TissueBox, turn right along the FloorLamp on the wooden table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight and turn right to enter into the living room and walk towards the tvstand.
Take the tissuebox from the table.
Turn left and take few steps and enter into the bedroom in right hand side. Go straight to reach the floorlamp.
Turn on the floorlamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the TissueBox by the light of a FloorLamp.

high_descs: Wall pass the hallway to get into the tvstand in the living room.
Pick up the tissuebox on the table in the living room.
take the tissue to the floorlamp in the bedroom.
Turn the floorlamp on in the bedroom.
anns.task_desc: Go to the living room and get a TissueBox for the bedroom.
